        <body>
            <p rend="align(center)"><sic>Trutee</sic> Room Congregation Bnai Israel</p>
            <p rend="align(center)"><date>Tebet the 15th 5617</date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">At a General Meeting of the members of the above<lb/> Congregation
                it was unanimously resolved.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Resolved that the thanks of this<lb/> Congregation are due to the
                    <persName>Rev. Isaac Leeser</persName><lb/> for the many favors and assistance
                rendered<lb/> to the Congn; And the said members highly<lb/> appreciate the various
                discourses addressed<lb/> to them in their Synagogue; And whereas the<lb/> Revd
                Gentleman has caused a great impression<lb/> on the mind of the members of this
                Congn at<lb/> the Consecration of their Synag: by an address<lb/> delivered on that
                occasion. Be it resolved<lb/> that to the Said <persName>Rev: Isaac
                    Leeser</persName> as a<lb/> mark of their high respect a Seat for life<lb/> be
                granted and all privileges as a contributing<lb/> member. Resolved that a copy of
                the foregoing<lb/>
                <sic>he send</sic> to the <persName>Rev. Mr Leeser</persName>, and inserted<lb/> in
                the Occident.</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">From the minutes</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)"><placeName>Philada</placeName>
                <date>Tebet 19/5617 Jany</date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">the <date>15/1857</date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">
                <persName role="author">Simon C Noah</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">assist. Secretary</p>
            <p>Rev &amp; Dr Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I have to repeat that in consequence<lb/> of having
                    <sic>hurted</sic> my finger I am prevented in writing<lb/> the above in a more
                &amp; better suitable style. You will<lb/> however perceive that the substance of
                the above emanates<lb/> from the body, and you may add to the above whatever<lb/>
                you may deem proper, in order that your fame may<lb/> be the better known both here
                and on the other<lb/> side of the <placeName><sic>atlantic</sic></placeName>, but
                please to insert it in your next<lb/> number &amp; oblige yours Truly <persName
                    role="author">Simon C <hi rend="underline">Noah</hi></persName></p>
        </body>
